quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  59,17,"Laati batte mum en kan…ìe …ói…óa ko yiite saasoo…ìe toon, …óuum ko njo…ìdi too√±oo…ìe"
  59,18,"Eehey mon goon…óibe ndeente Alla, yo fittaandu ndaar kondu ardinani jannga kule Alla pellet Alla ko kumpatii…óo ko ngolloton ko"
  59,19,"Wote ngone hono …ìeen yejjit…ìe Alla, O yejjitini …ìe pittaali mum en ko …ìeen ngoni faasiqee…ìe"
  59,20,"Yim…ìe yiite e yim…ìe aljanna potatah, ko yim…ìe aljanna ngoni fool…ìe"
  59,21,Si min tellinna o quraana e dow hooseere ma a yiinde honde huli honde fetta ngam hulde Alla …ói tinndi emin piyani…ói yim…ìe ko ngam …ìe miijo
  59,22,"Ko kanko woni dewetee…óo dewetee…óo e goonga alah si wonah kanko, ganndo ko wirni e ka wirnaaki kank woni jom yurmeende huftadinnde e yurmeende heeriinde"
  59,23,Ko kanko Alla mbo dewetee…óo e goonga alah si wonah kanko laam…óo cenii…óo kis…óo goon…ói…óo kiilndii…óo teddu…óo cemmbin…óo maw…óo senaare woodanii Alla e ko…ìe ndenndinta mbo ko
  59,24,"Ko kanko woni Alla tag…óo gootnu…óo mbaadin…óo tagu woodanii mbo in…óe …ìur…óe mo∆¥∆¥ude, woodanii mbo ko woni e nder kammuuji e leydi ko kanko woni pooloowo mbo hay gooto foolatah √ëee√±∆¥u…óo"
